toggl_create_project

create a project

toggl_create_project(project_name = get_context_project(),
  api_token = get_toggl_api_token(), wid = get_workspace_id(),
  client = NULL)

Arguments

project_name

project name
api_token

the toggl api token#'
wid

workspace_id
client

client name

Examples

# NOT RUN {
toggl_create_project()
# }
